{"tid":2463623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得周星馳套西遊記吹大咗？","createTime":"2021-03-27T00:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T01:00:33.000Z","uid":73991,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"49b4b87386a28a91cbedfe514db65849f59e70db","tid":2463623,"uid":73991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:27:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sbWLUZptp8I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsbWLUZptp8I&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=833c5ee1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sbWLUZptp8I</a><br />\n呢廿年黎香港不停有人吹奏呢周星馳套西遊記，原來根本就係支那吹風落黎，香港人當年係完全唔buy呢套戲，仲要有人跟支那講呢套戲叫大話西遊，證明支那文化入侵得幾緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人可唔可以比少少骨氣拒絕支那文化入侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3aecab8c1f7652b0a7c0bfcbf7154e3ce1954a","tid":2463623,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:34:41.000Z","msg":"👌"},{"pid":"f96be6917e3e62d743ae6ff2c083a703057d87b5","tid":2463623,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:37:45.000Z","msg":"即係星爺拍少林足球嗰陣用人用得太盡？"},{"pid":"0b12679a53a28078956cb8642acc4a3a26062d82","tid":2463623,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:46:55.000Z","msg":"睇見少林足球、功夫啲人滿飛天嘅畫面，就唔想睇。"},{"pid":"082eb066c85d26cc39a7a843abaf82f78ba2e13a","tid":2463623,"uid":2719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:49:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾 &gt; 十年後上神枱 &gt; 十年後吹大咗"},{"pid":"e0799092967aacaa3ae91767bd47810d47f7101d","tid":2463623,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:54:06.000Z","msg":"唔覺有咩好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係吹大既"},{"pid":"dbea6e905d4bd1ef263d34cc4496c1fcec2f9ed0","tid":2463623,"uid":163302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:59:55.000Z","msg":"唔同年代既品味問題<br />\n老豆老母覺得無聊眼花<br />\n攪唔清點樣穿越法<br />\n又500年前又500年後咁<br />\n但個陣80後應該多數覺得好睇<br />\n<br />\n仲有回魂夜都有同樣情況<br />\n個代既人睇戲最好就係唔駛用腦<br />\n連少少都唔駛"},{"pid":"4c35b12d4c68b6032581ca67a4e0506e76f566cd","tid":2463623,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:00:33.000Z","msg":"本身響香港咁多套周星馳電影入面呢套係唔值得吹奏， 佢係響大陸紅呢套電影，印象中2千年初期，大陸無啦啦好紅咩一萬年果套對白，洗晒版咁樣，跟住香港紅番轉頭。"}]}